      <title>埃里安称“金发姑娘”就业报告取悦美联储和市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/el-erian-says-goldilocks-jobs-april-report-to-please-fed-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mohamed El-Erian 在美国 4 月份就业数据公布后表示，劳动力市场的降温应该会给美联储带来可喜的缓解，因为美联储希望让美国经济软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/el-erian-says-goldilocks-jobs-april-report-to-please-fed-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 13:14:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
